## Levant region hosts 6 karst springs from 3 countries.

Lebanese and Syrian karst springs data are obtained from the WOKAS database. 

Israeli data is obtained from 2 different sources:

Daily discharge data are obtained from the WOKAS database "https://github.com/iGW-TU-Dresden/WoKas".
Monthly discharge data are provided by Avi Burg (burg@gsi.gov.il).

Original data provider for the Israeli karst springs is the National Hydrometeorological Service of Israel "https://data.gov.il/he/datasets/water_authority/spring_discharge/"

For further information, please see Metadata table.
